children.name: Duration
children.text:
End of Your Next Turn
(No Concentration)

children.name: Effects
children.text:
A magical boost fills you with confidence and protection as kind words lift your spirit. You gain the following effects until the end of your next turn:
- You have advantage on your next attack roll, ability check, or saving throw.
- Attacks made against you have disadvantage.
- Any healing you receive during this time is maximized, as though the highest possible result was rolled for each healing die.
